Path: This week in Nu #70
Content:
jonathandturner added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2802] ``set-env``
 command
 for setting environment variables in scope, added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2803] ``source``
 command
 for running a script in the current context/scope, simplified 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2805] ``if``
 to be standalone rather than stream-based
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2808] experimental support for flags in custom commands
, added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2814] custom subcommands
scrabsha fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2813] broken links in the README
